description: Drafts a U.S. franchise-focused confidentiality and non-disclosure agreement protecting franchisor operational manuals, financial data, marketing strategies, supplier terms, and trade secrets during pre-franchise discussions. Use when preparing an NDA for prospective franchisees, pre-FDD disclosures, franchise due diligence, or confidentiality agreements covering franchise system information. Trigger keywords: franchise NDA, confidentiality agreement, non-disclosure, FDD, prospective franchisee.
